author: Johann Wolfgang von Goethe
message: If you must tell me your opinions, tell me what you believe in. I have plenty of douts of my own.
title: Thought of the day

author: Ovid
message: Chance is always powerful. Let your hook be always cast; in the pool where you least expect it, there will be a fish.
title: Thought of the day

author: Og Mandino
message: I seek constantly to improve my manners and graces, for they are the sugar to which all are attracted.
title: Thought of the day

author: James Barrie
message: We never understand how little we need in this world until we know the loss of it.
title: Thought of the day
